  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nSync Altona and the process suspends, there are a couple of `response timeout` errors\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\nSync Altona\r\n\r\n**Logs**\r\nThis seems to be too slow to detect req/resp timeout as it took almost 1h (09:51:11 - 10:49:34):\r\n```\r\n2020-07-10 09:51:11  [NETWORK]       verbose: sending beacon_blocks_by_range request to 16Uiu2HAm6FBad3xnXj4WkkjpjaQQedn4rCmh8jCww2uw6MSSFNs2 requestId=6d3dc33918668bed, encoding=ssz_snappy\r\n...\r\n2020-07-10 10:49:34  [NETWORK]         error: failed to send request 6d3dc33918668bed to peer 16Uiu2HAm6FBad3xnXj4WkkjpjaQQedn4rCmh8jCww2uw6MSSFNs2 Error: response timeout\r\nError: response timeout\r\n    at nextAbortHandler (/Users/tuyennguyen/Projects/workshop/lodestar/node_modules/abortable-iterator/index.js:37:20)\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis seems to be too fast to detect req/resp timeout as it happens in same second (10:52:26):\r\n```\r\n2020-07-10 10:52:26  [NETWORK]       verbose: sending beacon_blocks_by_range request to 16Uiu2HAmV2BjFPcY4QYRuWE5DxpS2KpfLogiSmVKe9Lp9mTt3XBU requestId=2e576ea0a9ed7b15, encoding=ssz_snappy\r\n...\r\n2020-07-10 10:52:26  [NETWORK]         error: failed to send request 2e576ea0a9ed7b15 to peer 16Uiu2HAmV2BjFPcY4QYRuWE5DxpS2KpfLogiSmVKe9Lp9mTt3XBU Error: response timeout\r\nError: response timeout\r\n    at nextAbortHandler (/Users/tuyennguyen/Projects/workshop/lodestar/node_modules/abortable-iterator/index.js:37:20\r\n```\r\n",
